sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Clerk
    participant WebApp as "apps/web"
    participant ConvexBackend as "packages/backend"

    Browser->>WebApp: Navigates to /sign-in
    WebApp->>Browser: Renders Clerk's <SignIn /> component
    Browser->>Clerk: User enters credentials (e.g., email/password or social login)
    Clerk-->>Browser: Authenticates user and issues JWT
    Clerk->>WebApp: Redirects user to application
    
    WebApp->>ConvexBackend: Makes API request with JWT
    ConvexBackend->>ConvexBackend: Verifies JWT using auth.config.ts
    alt JWT is valid
        ConvexBackend->>WebApp: Returns data
    else JWT is invalid
        ConvexBackend->>WebApp: Returns authentication error
    end
